r really thought@about it before..."},{"chara":[{"id":200601,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104214/vo_full_913216-030-7"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyoko","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]But it makes some sense, y'know?"},{"chara":[{"id":200601,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104214/vo_full_913216-030-8"},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200501}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyoko","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]The girls that started actin'@odd all just up and disappeared."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200601,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104214/vo_full_913216-030-9"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyoko","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I figured they died fightin' Witches@or something..."},{"autoTurnFirst":4.4,"autoTurnNoDelay":1,"chara":[{"id":200601,"voiceFull":"fullvoice/section_104214/vo_full_913216-030-10"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyoko","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]But if they turned into Witches...@That'd explain it all, right?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200601,"motion":100}]},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104214/vo_full_913216-030-11","voiceFullStop":"fullvoice/section_104214/vo_full_913216-030-10"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]R...right..."},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104214/vo_full_913216-030-12"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]But...that's still just a possibility."},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104214/vo_full_913216-030-13"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Kyubey never said anything like that..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200601,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104214/vo_full_913216-030-14"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyoko","textAvColor":"textKyoko","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Yeah, askin' him is the easiest way@to get answers."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200601,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104214/vo_full_913216-030-15"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyoko","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]But she told me I can't ever reveal this@to Kyubey."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200601,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104214/vo_full_913216-030-16"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyoko","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]So Mami, you ask him."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200501,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104214/vo_full_913216-030-17"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Me...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200601,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104214/vo_full_913216-030-18"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyoko","textAvColor":"textKyoko","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Give and take, y'know."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200601,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104214/vo_full_913216-030-19"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyoko","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Confirming if it's true or not is gonna@dramatically change our combat strategies."},{"chara":[{"id":200601,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104214/vo_full_913216-030-20"}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyoko","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I'm countin' on ya, Mami."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200501,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104214/vo_full_913216-030-21"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]S-sure..."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"deleteArmatureList":[1],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
